<style>
.visor {
    background-color: rgba(250,250,250,0.3);
    padding: 30px;
    text-align: center;
}
.visor .container {
    max-width: 600px;
}
.visor .container p {
    text-align: justify;
}
</style>
<span class="moderatorHolder">
    {{#link-to 'agency.detail.settings' agency tagName="span"}}
        <button class=" btn btn-default admin-settings-button"><i class="fa fa-cog" aria-hidden="true"></i> Settings</button>
    {{/link-to}}
    <div class="custom">
        {{#link-to 'index'}}<button class='btn btn-primary left'><i class='fa fa-bars fa-fw'></i>&nbsp;Menu</button>{{/link-to}}
        {{#link-to 'agency.detail.settings.metadata' agency}}<button class='btn btn-primary right'><i class='fa fa-cog fa-fw'></i>&nbsp;Settings</button>{{/link-to}}
        {{#link-to 'agency.detail.analytics' agency}}<button class='btn btn-primary right'><i class='fa fa-bar-chart fa-fw'></i>&nbsp;Analytics</button>{{/link-to}}
        {{#link-to 'agency.detail.create' agency}}<button class='btn btn-primary right'><i class='fa fa-institution fa-fw'></i>&nbsp;Create Grant</button>{{/link-to}}
        {{#link-to 'agency.detail' agency}}<button class='btn btn-primary right'><i class='fa fa-globe fa-fw'></i>&nbsp;Overview</button>{{/link-to}}
        <h1>Agency Administration</h1>
    </div>
</span>
<div class='visor'>
    <div class='container'>
        <p>Select an Agency from the dropdown to administrate for. If the desired agency is not listed, then the currently logged in user does not have the required permissions to coordinate for that agency.</p>
        <br>
        <select class="agencySelect form-control input-lg select" onchange={{action (mut agencyId) value="target.value"}}>
            <option>Select An Agency</option>
            {{#each agencies as |agencyChoice|}}
            <option selected={{eq agency agencyChoice}} value={{agencyChoice.id}}>{{agencyChoice.name}}</option>
            {{/each}}
        </select>
        <br>
        {{#link-to 'agency.detail' agencyId class='btn btn-primary btn-lg button-pos'}}
            <!--<button type='button' class='btn btn-primary btn-lg button-pos'>View Grants</button>-->
            View Grants
        {{/link-to}}
        <p>If the currently logged in user does not have the correct permissions, he or she may request those permissions from the Agency's administration.</p>
    </div>
</div>
